briefTitle: Pharmacokinetics of NPC-01 After Single Oral Administration in Healthy Female Volunteers
officialTitle: A Single Dose Pharmacokinetics Study of NPC-01 (1mg Norethisterone and 0.02mg Ethynyl Estradiol) in Healthy Female Volunteers
summary:
The purpose of this study is to assess the pharmacokinetic profiles of norethisterone and ethinyl estradiol after single oral administration of NPC-01 in healthy female volunteers.

Pharmacokinetics of norethisterone and ethinyl estradiol will be evaluated on the basis of AUC, Cmax, tmax, t1/2, MRT, kel and AUCâˆž.

primaryOutcome.measure: Area Under the Plasma Concentration Versus Time Curve (AUC) on Norethisterone of NPC-01
